{"tid":2042414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後好難用特區護照申請美國簽證了","createTime":"2020-05-29T21:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T09:28:42.000Z","uid":66351,"like":155,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6059e4789cd2afb3fec3f36f758c2a96fc1b3b65","tid":2042414,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T21:35:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一直以來<br />\n持有香港特區護照去拎美國簽證都易過上面班蝗好多<br />\n<br />\n但今次侵侵對香港同支那一視同仁<br />\n姐係簽證會比現狀難批好多好多</span><br />\n<br />\n無論 旅遊簽證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 工作簽證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學生簽證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都會難批好多<br />\n<br />\n變相<br />\n如果想去美國讀書工作旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國政府好大好大機會唔批俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然啦<br />\n都有好多支那人去美國讀書工作旅行<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但申請成功率係相對地低好多<br />\n而申請手續都嚴好撚多<br />\n所有近親工作入息都會check<br />\n驚你地係間諜吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我地可以預料 <br />\n之後申請美國任何簽證的成功率都會 比依家低<br />\n要有定心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"c4ac56a2736eeb61d0155424f453c06914d96e88","tid":2042414,"uid":66351,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T21:39:09.000Z","msg":"申請美國簽證時<br />\n我地會填Hong Kong, Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n但好快 <br />\n我地要填Hong Kong, Chi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Na<br />\n<br />\n攬炒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"